What price should we set for the micropayment?
If we set the price so that it will yield the same total revenue as a
subscription, then <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Tom</ENAMEX> Average will pay the same amount either way. <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Jeff</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Accidental</ENAMEX> will save a bundle by buying occasional articles instead of having
