billing option known as the subscription or flat-price deal. It won't take a
genius <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">competitor</ENAMEX> to come up with this plan. Charging a usage-based fee for
content sounds fair--but it is artificial, because your costs are fixed. A
flat-rate <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">competitor</ENAMEX> would present an attractive proposition to <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Joe Avid</ENAMEX> and
